    {
      "id": "text_box_4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 295,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "功能流程\n\n1. 用户输入温度数据 (例如: 25.1 24.8 26.3 5.2 27.2 32.5 24.5)\n2. 系统解析并存储到 TemperatureData\n3. TemperatureAnalyzer 分析数据:\n   - findMax() → 32.5℃ (高温故障)\n   - findMin() → 5.2℃ (传感器异常)\n   - getAbnormalTemps() → 返回 [5.2, 32.5]\n4. 打印结果到控制台",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
